trans-unit.source: Specifies the mode for the automatic completion feature used in the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Especifica o modo para o recurso de preenchimento automático usado nos controles <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> e <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" />.

trans-unit.source: Appends the remainder of the most likely candidate string to the existing characters, highlighting the appended characters.
trans-unit.target: Acrescenta o restante da cadeia de caracteres candidata mais provável aos caracteres existentes, realçando os caracteres acrescentados.

trans-unit.source: Disables the automatic completion feature for the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Desabilita o recurso de preenchimento automático para os controles <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.ComboBox" /> e <see cref="T:System.Windows.Forms.TextBox" />.

trans-unit.source: Displays the auxiliary drop-down list associated with the edit control.
trans-unit.target: Exibe a lista suspensa auxiliar associada ao controle de edição.

trans-unit.source: This drop-down is populated with one or more suggested completion strings.
trans-unit.target: Essa lista suspensa é populada com uma ou mais cadeias de caracteres de conclusão sugeridas.

trans-unit.source: Applies both <see langword="Suggest" /> and <see langword="Append" /> options.
trans-unit.target: Aplica-se às opções <see langword="Suggest" /> e <see langword="Append" />.
